  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "The transaction involves the administration by the Asian Development Bank (ADB) of an equity investment of up to $4,000,000 or its Nepalese rupee equivalentwith an initial investment of up to $1,500,000 or its Nepalese rupee equivalentin InnoCSR Co. Ltd. (InnoCSR), a company headquartered in Seoul, Republic of Korea. The investment is to be provided by the ADB Ventures Investment Fund 1 under the ADB Ventures Financing Partnership Facility. The balance of the approved amount may be invested as equity or quasi-equity in subsequent fundraising rounds that InnoCSR is expected to undertake. Consistent with the established fund documents, ADB will not invest its own capital alongside the fund."
    },
    "ne": null
  },
